lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ac2be3d66092dd54dd70a14a572eb1ceafb785","tid":2396017,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"李官質疑原告為何建議10天審期，指本案案情簡單，也有影片及供詞為證，證人出庭作供的時間理應不長。李官又謂，原告是攝影師助理，案發時正在工作，並非在場投擲汽油彈；若然原告當時真的如被告一方所言以鋁梯襲警，其行為是否必要武力，將是審訊時其中一個關注之處。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/APT5OBV7AZA6PP2MIDRPSXIPDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FAPT5OBV7AZA6PP2MIDRPSXIPDE%2F&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjLhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=3f438908\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FAPT5OBV7AZA6PP2MIDRPSXIPDE%2F&h=6547d2cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/APT5OBV7AZA6PP2MIDRPSXIPDE/</a>"},{"pid":"01e8f6866b398a346ee2a2ffb6f6c8b48a55cd88","tid":2396017,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"自己衰左就和解？屌你老母啦死黑警"},{"pid":"9f5956a3eb9f03a01ddf56d85dcc542a59b032f5","tid":2396017,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6773d86672bce1476cc5a5f4bb1de68a168e676","tid":2396017,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"又想玩枱底,印尼女記者之前又係咁"}]}